{"tid":2038840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登小氣簿upupup p牌日經","createTime":"2020-05-27T17:59:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T18:01:25.000Z","uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"50166f5f52814652180cb628bfea99ca87645874","tid":2038840,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T17:59:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n做足安全措施，戴頭盔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以下呢d嘢由p牌仔提出好似好無說服力<br />\n但係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\np牌係唔可以睇小自己嘅潛能<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n歡迎起我底 我在連登的日子<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />正題黎喇<br />\n<br />\n連登群魔亂舞 五毛PR藍絲狗扮人<br />\n我要鬥佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n鬥佢老母重要法則<br />\n前事不忘後事之師<br />\n<del>死仆街仔唔好同我玩汁到寶捉虱<br />\n又帶風向黃絲乜乜乜</del>經典<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一步 必先利其器 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小氣簿<br />\n<br />\n今日起，見到五毛PR狗扮人<br />\nmark7佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nblock7佢？<br />\n佢地真係好L煩，搞到連登烏煙瘴氣<br />\nblock7曬六根清淨乾淨曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得你個版面係乾淨咋<br />\n其他連登仔，又例如我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n初黎報到，真係仆街仔橫飛<br />\n<br />\n點解連登好似越黎越少正常po？<br />\n連解出現連衛兵？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個詞姑勿論邊個最先提出，搵邊個提？<br />\n傻的嗎？<br />\n要鬥都係鬥死小氣簿入面嘅仆街仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Block7 姐係放生</span></span></span><br />\n縱容佢吸納新仔壯大自己圈子<br />\n流失更多覺得連登已經玩完嘅人<br />\n結果就係而家連登界面<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講咩都錯<br />\n<br />\n事實係，仲有人唔捨得呢度<br />\n正常po幾千li ke係事實<br />\n五毛PR狗扮人你試舉例大我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n衰嘢我只會舉對家嘢黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔識講漂亮話分析得好似其他巴絲咁好J<br />\n但係係香港長大嘅大家<br />\n我相信你地<br />\n因為大家都係自由而生<br />\n有最自由嘅靈魂 最自由嘅思考<br />\n所以我會相信大家嘅自由言論<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小氣簿就係為大家創造自由空間嘅利器<br />\n<br />\n第二步 Social distance 兩秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以我自己為例<br />\n我口水多過茶，最鍾意亂up<br />\n我好鍾意呢度<br />\n因為呢度比到自由我做自己<br />\n亦因為好鍾意呢度<br />\n我好擔心自己會捲入五毛pr狗扮人狗咬狗遊戲<br />\n經典<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />情緒道德綁架<br />\n<br />\n捲入去呢d遊戲，最經典莫過於綁架你自由嘅靈魂<br />\n令你唔可以自由講想講嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n實例，又係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我是個好好奇的孩子<br />\n乜po都鍾意入去八卦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n汁都撈埋<br />\n<br />\n最鍾意流連最新，大部分最新都會click入去，實在係太juicy<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日發芽痕想覆po<br />\np牌惡L曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />pish唔到無問題<br />\nYoung me too simple to naive<br />\n就係咁，我就被同一個po同一個X<del>唔知咩物種佢無答我</del>話我係網軍左膠xx<del>唔記得</del><br />\n好奇心有問題嗎<br />\n我的心傷透了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於佢唔答我問題，本著尋根究底嘅精神，加埋呢隻x物種嘅邀請，我就入佢po<br />\n佢一見到我即刻xx來了<del>個詞太傷我心了唔記得</del><br />\n果一刻我頓悟<br />\n我無嘢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我只係問問題姐 問嘢都唔比<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出現喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />估唔到呢個感嘆會出現係我個腦<br />\n揮之不去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就係咁我自由嘅靈魂受到入侵，言語自由受到侵害<br />\n<br />\n或許大家會建議我繼續反駁<br />\n被標籤xx<del>我真的忘記了太傷心選擇性失憶</del><br />\n重有，我無忘記自己咩身世<br />\n我只係一隻p<br />\n被標籤xx+p<br />\n我講咩無用，佢嘅黨羽/追隨者一定大把巴車埋黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我個朵被路人看見了何其肉酸，更加屈打成招<br />\n<blockquote><blockquote>問題時間：<br />\n哪個物種最喜歡屈打成招</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n我真係只係問問題同該物種講嘅嘢<br />\n稱呼佢一聲澳巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n竟然換黎網軍xx左膠人身攻擊<br />\n我心傷透了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n傷心事一浪接一浪<br />\n<br />\n有條友無同我交流之下<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />reported 拉<br />\n<br />\n咩係reported？好奇的我即刻去查<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好好整理完情緒，我思考<br />\n何解唔係block？<br />\n佢討厭我唔係應該無眼屎乾淨？<br />\n我得出個答案<br />\n佢想見到我 佢需要我<br />\n我會成為佢嘅戰鬥力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無限輪迴批鬥漩渦<br />\n消磨我精神意志同時間<br />\n<br />\n我會唔會驚左<br />\n選擇唔講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n傻的嗎。果次講唔到嘢已經傷透了<br />\n唔講嘢會屈死 我自由的靈魂啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝教導<br />\n逃避不是辦法<br />\n直擊要害才是真理<br />\n<br />\n典解佢會一下子就明言reported？<br />\n1. mark7 instead of block7<br />\n2. 打擊我弱小心靈<br />\n3. 話比人聽此人要不得<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝教導<br />\n1. 小氣簿 mark7<br />\n2. 回覆任何po 保持social distance 2秒<br />\n我無嘢講..................住<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我認得你<br />\n<br />\n第三步 直擊要害<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n新po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />9衝我鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新事物真係好多驚喜<br />\n打獵 小氣簿fa tfa t<br />\n儲得越多驚喜越多<br />\n我左眼見到鬼吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />鬼打鬼<br />\n新po保持so cial distance 我無嘢講....住<br />\n隔岸觀火好好食<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔同物種互相廝殺鬧到上熱門<br />\n甚至殺到敵我不分要同門漏口提點<br />\n好睇過CCTVB<del>so l y cctvb一d都唔好睇</del><br />\n<br />\n廝殺何解要上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />存在感<br />\n存在感<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要害<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以柔制剛<br />\n想我答爹<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />傻的嗎<br />\n我要狠狠地直擊要害 扼殺你在搖籃裡"},{"pid":"c89c4d973d21b62c3ef65bd8fbd9900adb481a93","tid":2038840,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T18:00:11.000Z","msg":"溫柔是我最大武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n縱然我很想加把口，<br />\n我唔忍心見到你地同門廝殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但是，家家有本難唸的經<br />\n我要以最溫柔嘅心包容你地<br />\n我要以最溫柔嘅心靜靜地看著你們<br />\n食花生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁就為之扼殺在搖籃裏<br />\n<br />\n咁，何解大熱門總缺席<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />存在感<br />\n<br />\n大熱門總缺席，<br />\n因為 真。連登仔一定多過佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無存在感敗走<br />\n運氣好嘅話，遇到個小氣仔，一定會狠狠地屌到佢體無完膚，真係好無存在價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無存在感=無存在價值 根據某物種lo gi c<br />\nPR你失業了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" clas